value.original: Import Product Cost to define the latest costing at the begining of accounting period. By providing the product cost you are allowed to see the valued stock value, and also post the 1st Goods Receipt document. Beside that, you will get matched value of your inventory in the warehouse and in your balance sheet.

value.original: Import business partner balance, to enable you register the payment from/lto your business partner after opening balance. You may not enter the detail of invoice, but you define how much and when you need to receive/pay to your business partner. One business partner can have several due date and amount to be received/paid.
